---
// InteractiveGraph.astro
// Vitruvian Column & Digital Brain Dashboard for ISAN Atelier Academiae
---
<div class="digital-brain-wrapper glass-panel">
  <div class="brain-header">
    <div class="header-accent"></div>
    <div class="title-area">
      <h3>🏛️ Panel de Control: Columna de Vitruvio</h3>
      <p class="subtitle">Ecosistema Cognitivo y Sincronización Neuronal Axial en Tiempo Real</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="search-box">
      <input type="text" id="node-search" placeholder="🔍 Buscar en la red (ej. Esfinge, Bitácora)..." />
      <span class="search-clear" id="search-clear" style="display: none;">&times;</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="digital-brain-grid">
    <!-- Left Column: D3 Graph Viewport -->
    <div class="graph-viewport-container">
      <div id="graph-container" class="graph-container"></div>
      
      <!-- Floating Zoom Controls -->
      <div class="graph-controls glass-panel">
        <button id="zoom-in" title="Acercar">+</button>
        <button id="zoom-out" title="Alejar">-</button>
        <button id="zoom-reset" title="Restablecer Vista">⟲</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column: Vitruvian Column Console -->
    <div class="vitruvian-console">
      
      <!-- Section A: Node Data Sheet -->
      <div class="console-section node-details-section">
        <h4>📋 Ficha Metrológica</h4>
        <div class="node-details-container">
          <div class="details-placeholder" id="details-placeholder">
            <div class="pulse-dot"></div>
            <p>Selecciona un nodo de la red para decodificar su metadato y comprobar su integridad.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="details-content" id="details-content" style="display: none;">
            <div class="tag-row">
              <span class="node-tag" id="details-category">CATEGORÍA</span>
              <span class="crypto-badge">
                <span class="badge-dot"></span> VERIFIED
              </span>
            </div>
            <h4 id="details-title">Título del Nodo</h4>
            <p id="details-desc">Descripción del nodo en el búnker.</p>
            <div class="details-footer">
              <a href="#" id="details-link" class="details-btn" target="_blank">Explorar Documento &rarr;</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section B: The Vitruvian Column (Linguistic Fluctuations) -->
      <div class="console-section vitruvian-column-section">
        <h4>🧬 Columna de Vitruvio (Ergonomía)</h4>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Procesamiento visual periférico de modos lingüísticos</p>
        
        <div class="vitruvian-bar-container">
          <div class="bar-label-row">
            <span class="bar-name">🎭 Modo Poético</span>
            <span class="bar-value" id="poetic-val">50%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar-track">
            <div class="bar-fill poetic-bar" id="poetic-bar" style="width: 50%;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vitruvian-bar-container">
          <div class="bar-label-row">
            <span class="bar-name">🐍 Modo Hermético</span>
            <span class="bar-value" id="hermetic-val">60%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar-track">
            <div class="bar-fill hermetic-bar" id="hermetic-bar" style="width: 60%;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vitruvian-bar-container">
          <div class="bar-label-row">
            <span class="bar-name">💻 Modo Técnico</span>
            <span class="bar-value" id="technical-val">75%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar-track">
            <div class="bar-fill technical-bar" id="technical-bar" style="width: 75%;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vitruvian-bar-container">
          <div class="bar-label-row">
            <span class="bar-name">📖 Modo Narrativo</span>
            <span class="bar-value" id="narrative-val">45%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar-track">
            <div class="bar-fill narrative-bar" id="narrative-bar" style="width: 45%;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section C: Cryptographic Integrity Box -->
      <div class="console-section integrity-section">
        <h4>🔑 Consola de Integridad S.S.</h4>
        <div class="hash-box">
          <div class="hash-label">HASH INTEGRIDAD SHA-256 (hash_m7)</div>
          <div class="hash-value" id="integrity-hash">a68d716cf9ef673196f7c6e61f215e98516ee71a7d65691e847c1ba0c18d18f4</div>
        </div>
        <div class="integrity-footer">
          <span class="standard-label">Estándar: <strong>ISAN-2026</strong></span>
          <span class="status-label">Resonancia: <strong id="resonancia-val">1.57714881</strong></span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.digital-brain-wrapper {
  margin: 2.5rem 0;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
  border: 1px solid var(--color-glass-border);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
  border-radius: 12px;
}

.brain-header {
  padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.05) 0%, transparent 100%);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-glass-border);
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 1rem;
  position: relative;
}

.header-accent {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 180px;
  height: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-digital-cyan), var(--color-neural-red));
}

.title-area h3 {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 1.35rem;
  color: white;
  letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.25);
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
}

.subtitle {
  margin: 0.2rem 0 0 0;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
}

.search-box {
  position: relative;
  max-width: 280px;
  width: 100%;
}

.search-box input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 0.55rem 2rem 0.55rem 1rem;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-glass-border);
  border-radius: 20px;
  color: white;
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.search-box input:focus {
  outline: none;
  border-color: var(--color-digital-cyan);
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.3);
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
}

.search-clear {
  position: absolute;
  right: 12px;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
}

/* Grid Layout for Vitruvian Dashboard */
.digital-brain-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.7fr 1.3fr;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #050811 0%, #020307 100%);
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .digital-brain-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}

.graph-viewport-container {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 580px;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--color-glass-border);
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .graph-viewport-container {
    height: 460px;
    border-right: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-glass-border);
  }
}

.graph-container {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  cursor: grab;
}

.graph-container:active {
  cursor: grabbing;
}

/* Floating Zoom Controls */
.graph-controls {
  position: absolute;
  top: 1rem;
  right: 1rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 5px;
  padding: 5px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  z-index: 10;
  background: rgba(4, 6, 12, 0.85);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-glass-border);
}

.graph-controls button {
  width: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: 6px;
  color: white;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: bold;
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.graph-controls button:hover {
  background: rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.2);
  border-color: var(--color-digital-cyan);
  color: var(--color-digital-cyan);
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.3);
}

/* Vitruvian Sidebar Console */
.vitruvian-console {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.25rem;
  padding: 1.25rem;
  background: rgba(4, 6, 12, 0.45);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  max-height: 580px;
  overflow-y: auto;
  border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .vitruvian-console {
    max-height: none;
    border-left: none;
  }
}

.console-section {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.console-section:hover {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025);
  border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
}

.console-section h4 {
  margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: white;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  padding-bottom: 0.4rem;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.section-subtitle {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  margin: -0.5rem 0 1rem 0;
}

/* Ficha de Nodo details container */
.node-details-container {
  min-height: 110px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
}

.details-placeholder {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  gap: 0.8rem;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
}

.pulse-dot {
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  background-color: var(--color-digital-cyan);
  border-radius: 50%;
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--color-digital-cyan);
  animation: pulse-dot 1.5s infinite ease-in-out;
}

.tag-row {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.node-tag {
  background: rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.07);
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.15);
  padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-digital-cyan);
}

.crypto-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 4px;
  background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
  border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
  color: #10b981;
  padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.badge-dot {
  width: 5px;
  height: 5px;
  background: #10b981;
  border-radius: 50%;
  box-shadow: 0 0 6px #10b981;
}

#details-title {
  margin: 0.2rem 0 0.4rem 0;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: white;
  font-weight: bold;
  letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

#details-desc {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  line-height: 1.45;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
  margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
}

.details-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.2) 0%, rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.05) 100%);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-digital-cyan);
  color: white !important;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  border-radius: 4px;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
  text-align: center;
}

.details-btn:hover {
  background: var(--color-digital-cyan);
  color: black !important;
  box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.4);
}

/* Vitruvian Neon Chromatic Bars */
.vitruvian-bar-container {
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.vitruvian-bar-container:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.bar-label-row {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.bar-name {
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
  font-weight: 500;
}

.bar-value {
  font-family: monospace;
  font-weight: bold;
  color: var(--color-digital-cyan);
}

.bar-track {
  width: 100%;
  height: 6px;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  border-radius: 3px;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
}

.bar-fill {
  height: 100%;
  border-radius: 3px;
  transition: width 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  position: relative;
}

.poetic-bar {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ec4899, #f43f5e);
  box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.5);
}

.hermetic-bar {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6366f1, #a855f7);
  box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.5);
}

.technical-bar {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00f2ff, #10b981);
  box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.5);
}

.narrative-bar {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fbbf24, #f97316);
  box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.5);
}

/* Crypto Integrity Box */
.hash-box {
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.hash-label {
  font-size: 0.58rem;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.hash-value {
  font-family: monospace;
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  color: #10b981;
  word-break: break-all;
  letter-spacing: -0.2px;
  line-height: 1.25;
}

.integrity-footer {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
}

.integrity-footer strong {
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
}

@keyframes pulse-dot {
  0% { transform: scale(0.9); opacity: 0.6; }
  50% { transform: scale(1.2); opacity: 1; box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--color-digital-cyan); }
  100% { transform: scale(0.9); opacity: 0.6; }
}
</style>

